# 7. みんなで一緒に

Tsukasa: Do you see them anywhere?!
Airi: No, I'm not seeing them.
Mafuyu: The parade seems to be about half over. At this rate...
Miyake: I guess we're not gonna be able to watch it together...
Tsukasa: No, don't give up...! It's not over yet! If we just keep looking...
Tourists: Wow...! What is that?! It's so pretty!
Tourists: Wait, it's snowing! But just around that girl...! How are they doing that?!
Tsukasa: It's snowing...?
Mafuyu: How's that possible...?
Airi: Hey...! Isn't that Shizuku?!
Tourists: I don't believe it... That girl with the white haori looks like a real yuki-onna...
Tourists: I can't believe they're getting it to snow!
Tourists: Wait, she looks familiar... Where have I seen her before...?
Rui: Okay, Hinomori. Ready?
Shizuku: Yes...!
Shizuku: (Just like Kamishiro said. Raise your right arm and...)
Rui: (Now! Full power!)
Tourists: Whoa! She's making more snow!
Rui: Perfect...!
Rui: (Please, everyone! It's us...!)
Tsukasa: Haha...
Tsukasa: Hah hah hah hah! I should expect no less from our director! Bravo!
Airi: Don't forget about Shizuku! That frosty look on her face... It's like she's the real thing!
Mafuyu: Hehe. It's certainly hard to miss them.
Tsukasa: Rui! Shizuku! We're over here!
Shizuku & Rui: ...!
Shizuku: Kamishiro, I see Tsukasa and the others...!
Rui: Yes, I just saw them as well!
Airi: We'll wait for you guys at the end!
Shizuku: Okay!
Tsukasa: I have to say, Rui, your idea was spectacular!
Airi: Yeah, I don't think any of us were expecting you to make yourselves seen like that.
Mafuyu: Yes, not only was it unexpected, but you had all the other onlookers completely captivated.
Miyake: You totally blew everyone away! You really are a genius, Kamishiro...!
Rui: Hehe. I feel honored.
Rui: However, if all eyes were really on us...
Tourists: I wasn't really sure when she walked past us, but isn't that Shizuku Hinomori...?
Tourists: Yeah, it's gotta be her! Wanna go say hi?
Airi: ...! This could get messy.
Tsukasa: Nonsense. All we have to do is use this crowd for cover.
Announcement: Next! Here come the professionals!
Tsukasa: Ah, perfect timing!
Tsukasa: Now, let's enjoy this parade together!
Mafuyu, Shizuku & Airi: Yeah! Yes!
Tsukasa: Whoa! I don't think these count as costumes anymore! They look like real spirits from folklore!
Rui: Yes, they're very realistic. I believe they're inspired by namahage.
Miyake: Those ogres look absolutely amazing!
Shizuku: That rokurokubi...! Her neck just keeps growing longer and longer! How are they doing that...?!
Airi: Her head looks way too real!
Mafuyu: That person dressed as a tengu must have incredible balance. Their sandals look like stilts...
Hayashi: Whoa, it's a kuchisake-onna...
Taniyama: Imagine seeing one of those at night! I bet we'd all scream while running for our lives!
Miyake: Haha. I'm not sure we'd be that scared...
Rui: “Am I pretty...?”
Miyake, Hayashi & Taniyama: Whoa!
Hayashi: That was you, Kamishiro...?!
Taniyama: Geez, you really got us! Miyake even fell over!
Miyake: Th-That was mean, Kamishiro!
Rui: Hah hah hah! My apologies.
Tsukasa: Oh, Rui, look! The floats are coming! This must be the finale!
Tsukasa: It's like a climactic scene! All those spirits...! And only I, Tsukasa Tenma the Spirit Busting High Schooler can defeat them!
Rui: Hehe. In Kyoto no less. That certainly sounds like a fun action-adventure story.
Tsukasa: Exactly! Oh, and that black tengu would be the final boss! No, he'd be my enemy at first, but later my ally...
Rui: Hehe...
Rui: (I'm so glad I came...)
Rui: (Because I wouldn't have been able to see this event with them if I hadn't.)
Rui: (Not only that, our school trip is the only reason we did anything together at all.)
Rui: (So, for now...)
Rui: (I should enjoy this one-night-only performance.)
Rui: Well, I guess that's it for today...
Shizuku: Yes, quite a lot happened along the way, but it ended up being a wonderful day.
Airi: Thanks for having us, you guys!
Miyake: N-No... We should be the ones thanking you. You made the day just that much better.
Tsukasa: I agree! What we experienced today will surely remain in our album of memories for years to come!
Rui: Our album...
Shizuku: Hehe. I believe so too!
Mafuyu: Anyway, we'll see you all.
Rui: Everyone.
Rui: How about we take a group photo together?
Tsukasa: A group photo?
Rui: Yes. I'd like to have something to commemorate this day with.
Shizuku: Yes, I'd like that as well! Oh, but my phone's battery is still...
Airi: Then, we can use mine! I'll see if one of the staff can take it for us!
Tsukasa: Why this all of a sudden, Rui...? You never usually suggest doing anything like this.
Rui: Yes, I know.
Rui: But I thought it'd be nice to for a change.
Tsukasa: Yes, I agree!
Airi: Bunch together you guys! Get ready!
Staff Member: Okay, everyone! Say, “Cheese!”
